泉州酒店坍塌追踪：垮塌前在施工并发生柱子变形，酒店多次被罚。
Quanzhou Hotel collapse tracking: collapse before the construction and deformation of pillars, the hotel was repeatedly punished.
毛翊君。
Yijun Mao.
