为何将这座屡次被罚且所在建筑内部仍在装修的酒店定为疫情隔离观察点？3月7日晚，泉州鲤城区欣佳酒店所在的建筑发生楼体坍塌，楼内9人自行逃出，71人被困。
On the night of March 7, the building housing Xinjia Hotel in Quanzhou City collapsed, trapping nine people and trapping 71 others.
截至3月8日16时，已救出48人，其中10人死亡，余下38人分别送至四家定点医院救治。
As at 1600 hours on 8 March, 48 people had been rescued, of whom 10 had died, leaving 38 others in four designated hospitals.
截至发稿时，另有23人还在搜救中。
At the time of writing, another 23 people were still in search and rescue.
该楼的业主杨金锵已被公安部门控制。
The building's owner, Yang Jinqiang, is under police control.
泉州应急救援工作领导小组于3月8日召开两场发布会，通报了事件相关情况。
The Quanzhou Emergency Relief Leading Group held two briefings on the incident on 8 March.
据相关部门介绍，新冠肺炎疫情发生后，欣佳酒店被作为集中医学观察点，用以对来自重点疫区或有相关旅居史的人员，进行集中医学观察。
After the outbreak of New Crown Pneumonia, Xinjia Hotel was used as a centralized medical observation point for people from key epidemic areas or with relevant sojourn histories, according to relevant departments.
此次事件救援组副组长、鲤城区政府代区长苏延辉在3月8日下午的发布会上介绍，欣佳酒店坍塌时，楼内有接受观察人员58人，其中随行子女12人、返乡7人、务工37人、探亲2人。
At a press conference on the afternoon of March 8, Su Yanhui, deputy head of the incident rescue team and acting head of the Lei Cheng District Government, said there were 58 observers inside the building, including 12 accompanying children, 7 returning home, 37 migrant workers and 2 family visits.
所有人员在进入定点观察点之后，均已进行核酸检测，结果均为阴性。
All personnel were tested for nucleic acid after entering the sentinel observation point, and the results were negative.
此外，欣佳酒店还有管理、服务等人员16人，另有租在该栋大楼的车行人员6人。
In addition, there are 16 management, service and other staff, as well as six car dealerships in the building.
伤者被四家医院收治，分别为泉州市第一医院、福建医科大学附属第二医院、联勤保障部队第910医院、泉州市中医院。
The injured were admitted to four hospitals, namely Quanzhou City Hospital No. 1, Fujian Medical University Hospital No. 2, United Support Force Hospital No. 910, Quanzhou City Chinese Hospital.
联勤保障部队第910医院行政办公室人员告诉《中国新闻周刊》，他们接收的6名伤者目前有重症患者，也有轻症患者，至于哪些伤员被送到哪家医院，是由泉州市卫健委安排的。
Personnel from the 910 hospital administrative office told China News Weekly that the six casualties they had received were now seriously ill and had mild cases, and that the Quanzhou City Health Commission had arranged which of the injured had been taken to which hospital.
泉州市中医院行政部门一位值班人员回应《中国新闻周刊》称，他们接收的14名伤者都是轻伤。
A duty officer from the TCM administration in Quanzhou City responded to China News Weekly, saying the 14 injuries they had received were minor injuries.
3月8日上午，国家卫健委派出了中山大学附属第一医院神经外科、胸外科、骨显微外科、重症医学科等4名国家级专家抵达泉州，指导抢救。
On the morning of March 8, four state-level experts, including neurosurgery, thoracic surgery, bone microsurgery and severe medicine from Zhongshan University's First Affiliated Hospital, arrived in Quanzhou to guide rescue efforts.
医院对每名伤者进行血相、影像学等医学检查，对每位伤者实行“一人一室一团队”以及必要的心理疏导，伤者情势平稳。
Each injured person was examined by the hospital in the form of blood photographs, imaging and other medical examinations. Each injured person was given "one person, one room, one team" and necessary psychological counselling.
目前，现场保有15辆监护型救护车待命，并携有20名院前急救人员协助抢救。
Currently, there are 15 on-site surveillance ambulances on standby, with 20 pre-hospital first responders assisting in their rescue.
院前急救人员是指在院外对急危重症病人进行急救的医护人员。
Pre-hospital emergency personnel refers to the hospital outside the hospital to the critically ill patients emergency medical personnel.
另有市区专业队伍负责现场防控工作。
Another urban professional team is responsible for site prevention and control.
据相关部门了解，坍塌建筑建设于2013年，占地约5亩，主体7层，每层1000平方米，楼高22米，为钢结构建筑物。
According to the relevant departments, the collapse of construction in 2013, covering about 5 mu, the main 7th floor, 1000 square meters per floor, 22 meters high, steel structure buildings.
2018年改造为欣佳酒店，并于当年6月开业，酒店有各类客房共计66间。
Renovated as Xinjia Hotel in 2018 and opened in June of that year, the hotel has a total of 66 rooms.
事发前，该栋建筑内正在进行装修。
The building was being renovated before the incident.
垮塌前几分钟，有商户接到楼内施工人员电话，称进行作业时，一层的一根柱子发生变形。
Minutes before the collapse, a merchant received a telephone call from a builder inside the building, saying that a pillar on the ground floor had been deformed while working.
而泉州市鲤城区住建局局长张翼在事后对媒体称，该建筑一楼共有6间，其中两间原为超市，今年春节前，房屋业主将一楼出租的超市收回重新改装。
Before the Spring Festival holiday, the owner of the first floor of a six-storey building, two of which were former supermarkets, had taken back a supermarket rented from the first floor to remodel it, Zhang Wing, the bureau's secretary, told reporters.
而坍塌原因是装修引起还是楼体本身的结构问题，还需进一步甄别。
The collapse is caused by decoration or the structure of the building itself, still need to be further screened.
据公开资料显示，该酒店此前曾多次被处罚：2018年11月，因未按规定办理住宿登记，泉州市公安局鲤城分局曾责令其整改，并罚款3000元。
According to public information, the hotel had been punished several times before: in November 2018, the Lei Cheng branch of Quanzhou Public Security Bureau ordered the hotel to rectify and fined 3,000 yuan for failing to register the required accommodation.
2019年12月，因相同的问题受到相同的行政处罚。
In December 2019, the same administrative penalty was imposed for the same issue.
另外，在2019年7月，其还因未按照《个体工商户年度报告办法》规定报送年度报告，被泉州市工商行政管理局鲤城分局列入经营异常名录。
In addition, in July 2019, it was included in the list of operating anomalies by the Lei City Branch of the Quanzhou City Administration for Industry and Commerce for failing to submit annual reports as required by the Annual Report on Individual Chamber of Commerce and Industry.
2019年8月，其经营场所发生过一次变更，从该楼6楼变为一层大厅以及四至六层。
In August 2019, its premises were changed once, from the sixth floor of the building to the first floor lobby and four to six floors.
为何将这座屡次被罚且所在建筑内部仍在装修的酒店定为疫情隔离观察点？《中国新闻周刊》就此联系泉州市鲤城区疾病预防控制中心，一位办公室人员回应称，这是鲤城区卫健局做的安排。
Why is the hotel, which has been repeatedly ordered and the interior of the building still being renovated, a staff member of the office responded that the arrangement was made by the Lei Cheng Health Bureau in response to China News Weekly's communication with the Centre for Disease Control and Prevention in Lei City of Quanzhou City.
而鲤城区卫健局工作人员告诉《中国新闻周刊》，这是根据上一级的文件执行的，并不清楚选点的具体原因。
And Lei Cheng Wei Health Bureau staff told China News Weekly, which is based on the higher level of documentation, is not clear on the specific reasons for the selection.
3月8日下午，《中国新闻周刊》多次致电泉州市卫健委办公室，电话始终无人接听。
On the afternoon of March 8, China News Weekly called the office of the Quanzhou City Fitness Commission several times.
《中国新闻周刊》查询到，欣佳酒店在该垮塌建筑中占据4、5、6三层，该栋楼3层有一家名为琴悦公馆的足浴和名为小资生活吧的餐饮店。
The hotel occupies four, five and six floors of the collapsed building, according to China News Weekly. The three-storey building houses a foot bath called the Qin Yue residence and a restaurant called Little Capital Living Bar.
此外，楼内商户还包括福建省顶鑫再生资源回收有限公司、泉州全德宝汽车销售有限公司等。
In addition, the building also includes the Fujian Province Jingxin Renewable Resources Recycling Co. Ltd, Quanzhou Quanzhou Quande Auto Sales Co. Ltd.
3月8日下午，《中国新闻周刊》联系泉州全德宝汽车销售有限公司负责人，其称于2013年以4万元/月的租金，向房东杨金锵租下一层一半面积的店面，是最早在楼内经营的商户之一。
On the afternoon of March 8, China News Weekly contacted the head of Quanzhou Quandebao Automobile Marketing Co. Ltd., who claimed to have rented a half-floor storefront from his landlord, Yang Jinqiang, for $40,000 per month in 2013.
整栋楼内，除了他们，只有一家汽车维修公司，租用了一楼的剩余面积。
There was only one car repair company in the building, except for them, which rented the remaining space on the first floor.
全德宝汽车销售有限公司负责人告诉《中国新闻周刊》，直到2016年，房东杨金锵才开始招商，此前整栋楼只有钢架，从二层可以直接看到七层底部。
The head of Quande Bao Automobile Marketing Co., Ltd. told China News Weekly that until 2016, the landlord Yang Jin-qiang began to buy, the entire building only steel frame, from the second floor can be seen directly at the bottom of the seven-story.
那时，全德宝汽车销售有限公司将第七层作为公司的员工宿舍。
At that time, Quande Bao Automobile Sales Co. Ltd. as the seventh floor of the company's staff quarters.
而一层此前没有实墙，仅是玻璃门窗，柱子实为钢管外包木板。
The first floor before there is no real wall, just glass doors and windows, pillars for steel pipe outsourcing board.
2017年初，杨金锵开始装修欣佳酒店，用混凝土浇筑3层到6层地板，装修过程中，一楼的玻璃不断被震裂，上述租户向杨金锵反应无果，最后在当年年底搬离了该楼。
At the beginning of 2017, Yang Jinqiang began to decorate the Xinjia Hotel, pouring 3 to 6 floors with concrete. During the renovation process, the first floor of the glass was repeatedly broken, the above-mentioned tenants to Yang Jinqiang, and finally moved out of the building at the end of the year.
据相关工商资料显示，杨金锵于2018年注册登记该酒店。
According to relevant industrial and commercial information, Yang Jinshan registered the hotel in 2018.
杨金锵今年65岁，泉州本地人。
Yang Jinqiang, 65, is a native of Quanzhou.
其名下除了该酒店，还有泉州市新星机电工贸有限公司，其为法人，于2006年注册，注册资本330万元。
In addition to the hotel, Quanzhou New Star Electrical and Mechanical Industry Co., Ltd. is a legal person, registered in 2006, registered capital of 3.3 million yuan.
